msgid "List all vouchers"
msgstr "列出所有優惠券"

msgid ""
"Get all voucher codes. Customers see only active vouchers. Staff see all "
"vouchers with filtering by status and discount type. Supports search by code"
" or name."
msgstr "取得所有優惠券代碼。顧客僅能看到啟用中的優惠券。員工可以看到所有優惠券，並可根據狀態和折扣類型進行篩選。支援透過代碼或名稱進行搜尋。"

msgid "Create new voucher"
msgstr "建立新優惠券"

msgid ""
"Create a new voucher code (admin only). Specify discount type (percentage, "
"fixed, gift_card), value, validity dates, usage limits, and product/category"
" restrictions."
msgstr "建立新的優惠券代碼（僅限管理員）。請指定折扣類型（百分比、固定金額、禮品卡），價值，有效日期，使用限制，以及產品/類別限制。"

msgid "Get voucher details"
msgstr "取得優惠券詳情"

msgid ""
"Get detailed information about a specific voucher including discount rules, "
"usage limits, restrictions, and eligible products/categories."
msgstr "取得特定優惠券的詳細資訊，包括折扣規則、使用限制、限制條件以及合資格的產品/類別。"

msgid "Update voucher"
msgstr "更新優惠券"

msgid ""
"Update voucher configuration (admin only). Can modify discount value, dates,"
" usage limits, and restrictions. Active vouchers should be updated "
"carefully."
msgstr "更新優惠券設定（僅限管理員）。可以修改折扣值、日期、使用限制和限制條件。正在使用的優惠券應謹慎更新。"

msgid "Partially update voucher"
msgstr "部分更新優惠券"

msgid ""
"Update specific voucher fields (admin only). Useful for extending expiry "
"dates or adjusting usage limits without resending full voucher data."
msgstr "更新特定優惠券欄位（僅限管理員）。此功能可用於延長過期日期或調整使用限制，而無需重新傳送完整的優惠券資料。"

msgid "Delete voucher"
msgstr "刪除優惠券"

msgid ""
"Delete a voucher code (admin only). Warning: This permanently removes the "
"voucher and all usage history. Consider deactivating instead."
msgstr "刪除優惠券代碼（僅限管理員）。警告：這將永久刪除優惠券及其所有使用記錄。請考慮停用優惠券而非刪除。"

msgid "Validate voucher code"
msgstr "驗證優惠券代碼"

msgid ""
"Validate a voucher code and check if it can be used by the authenticated "
"user. Requires authentication to prevent enumeration attacks. Rate limited "
"to 10 requests/minute. Returns discount amount if cart total provided."
msgstr "驗證優惠券代碼並檢查是否可以被驗證用戶使用。需要驗證以防止枚舉攻擊。每分鐘限10次請求。如果提供了購物車總額，將返回折扣金額。"

msgid "Check customer eligibility"
msgstr "檢查客戶資格"

msgid ""
"Check if the authenticated user is eligible to use a specific voucher. "
"Validates usage limits, customer restrictions, and account requirements. "
"Rate limited to 10 requests/minute."
msgstr "檢查驗證用戶是否有資格使用特定優惠券。驗證使用限制、客戶限制和帳戶要求。每分鐘限10次請求。"

msgid "Calculate discount amount"
msgstr "計算折扣金額"

msgid ""
"Calculate the discount amount for a given cart total. Applies percentage or "
"fixed discount rules, minimum purchase requirements, and maximum discount "
"caps."
msgstr "計算特定購物車總額的折扣金額。適用百分比或固定折扣規則、最低購買要求以及最高折扣上限。"

msgid "Get voucher usage statistics"
msgstr "取得優惠券使用統計資料"

msgid ""
"Get detailed usage statistics for a voucher including total uses, unique "
"customers, total discount given, average discount per use, and recent usage "
"history."
msgstr "取得優惠券的詳細使用統計資料，包括總使用次數、獨特客戶數、總折扣金額、每次使用的平均折扣以及近期使用記錄。"

msgid "Bulk generate voucher codes"
msgstr "批量生成優惠券代碼"

msgid ""
"Bulk generate multiple voucher codes (admin only). Maximum 1000 codes per "
"request. All generated codes share the same discount rules and restrictions "
"but have unique codes."
msgstr "批量產生多個優惠券代碼（僅限管理員）。每次請求最多產生 1000 個代碼。所有產生的代碼共享相同的折扣規則和限制，但擁有獨特的代碼。"

msgid "List voucher usage history"
msgstr "列出優惠券使用歷史"

msgid ""
"Get voucher usage history for the authenticated user. Staff can view all "
"usage. Filter by voucher ID or user ID. Shows when voucher was used, "
"discount applied, and associated order."
msgstr ""
"取得已驗證用戶的優惠券使用歷史。工作人員可以查看所有使用記錄。可透過優惠券 ID 或用戶 ID 篩選。顯示優惠券使用時間、應用的折扣以及相關訂單。"

msgid "Get usage details"
msgstr "取得使用明細"

msgid ""
"Get detailed information about a specific voucher usage including timestamp,"
" user, order, discount amount applied, and voucher code used."
msgstr "取得特定優惠券使用詳情，包括時間戳、用戶、訂單、所套用的折扣金額以及使用的優惠券代碼。"

msgid "List gift cards"
msgstr "列出禮品卡"

msgid ""
"Get gift cards for the authenticated user. Shows gift cards purchased by "
"user or received by email. Staff can view all gift cards. Filter by status "
"(active, partially_used, fully_used, expired)."
msgstr ""
"取得已驗證用戶的禮品卡。顯示用戶購買或透過電子郵件收到的禮品卡。員工可以查看所有禮品卡。可按狀態篩選（active、partially_used、fully_used、expired）。"

msgid "Create gift card"
msgstr "建立禮品卡"

msgid ""
"Create a new gift card (admin only). Specify original value, recipient "
"email, optional message, and expiry date. Automatically generates unique "
"gift card code."
msgstr "建立新的禮品卡（僅限管理員）。指定原價值、收件人電子郵件、選項訊息和到期日。自動生成唯一的禮品卡代碼。"

msgid "Get gift card details"
msgstr "取得禮品卡詳情"

msgid ""
"Get detailed information about a specific gift card including original "
"value, current balance, recipient, status, and usage history."
msgstr "取得特定禮品卡的詳細資訊，包括原價值、當前餘額、收件人、狀態和使用記錄。"

msgid "Update gift card"
msgstr "更新禮品卡"

msgid ""
"Update gift card information (admin only). Can modify balance, status, or "
"expiry date. Use carefully as this affects customer balances."
msgstr "更新禮品卡資訊（僅限管理員）。可修改餘額、狀態或到期日。請謹慎使用，因為這會影響客戶餘額。"

msgid "Partially update gift card"
msgstr "部分更新禮品卡"

msgid ""
"Update specific gift card fields (admin only). Useful for extending expiry "
"date or adjusting status without sending full gift card data."
msgstr "更新特定禮品卡欄位（僅限管理員）。可用於延長到期日或調整狀態，而無需傳送完整的禮品卡資料。"

msgid "Delete gift card"
msgstr "刪除禮品卡"

msgid ""
"Delete a gift card (admin only). Warning: This permanently removes the gift "
"card and remaining balance. Ensure customer has been refunded if applicable."
msgstr "刪除禮品卡（僅限管理員）。警告：此操作將永久刪除禮品卡及其餘額。如適用，請確保已為客戶退款。"

msgid "Check gift card balance"
msgstr "查看禮品卡餘額"

msgid ""
"Check the current balance of a gift card by code. Returns original value, "
"remaining balance, currency, and status. Does not require owning the gift "
"card."
msgstr "透過代碼檢查禮品卡的當前餘額。返回原始價值、剩餘餘額、貨幣和狀態。無需擁有該禮品卡。"

msgid "Redeem gift card amount"
msgstr "兌換禮品卡金額"

msgid ""
"Redeem a specific amount from a gift card. Validates sufficient balance and "
"updates remaining balance. Returns new balance after redemption."
msgstr "從禮品卡中兌換特定金額。驗證足夠的餘額並更新剩餘餘額。兌換後返回新餘額。"

msgid "List voucher restrictions"
msgstr "列出優惠券限制"

msgid ""
"Get all voucher restrictions (admin only). Filter by voucher ID to see "
"restrictions for a specific voucher. Includes minimum purchase, customer "
"group, and usage limit rules."
msgstr "獲取所有優惠券限制（僅限管理員）。透過優惠券 ID 篩選以查看特定優惠券的限制。包括最低購買額、客戶群組和使用次數限制規則。"

msgid "Add voucher restriction"
msgstr "新增優惠券限制"

msgid ""
"Add a new restriction to a voucher (admin only). Can restrict by minimum "
"purchase amount, customer group, product category, or usage limits per "
"customer."
msgstr "為優惠券新增限制（僅限管理員）。可限制最低購買金額、顧客群組、產品類別或每位顧客的使用次數上限。"

msgid "Get restriction details"
msgstr "取得限制詳情"

msgid ""
"Get detailed information about a specific voucher restriction including "
"restriction type, conditions, and affected voucher."
msgstr "取得特定優惠券限制的詳細資訊，包括限制類型、條件和受影響的優惠券。"

msgid "Update restriction"
msgstr "更新限制"

msgid ""
"Update a voucher restriction (admin only). Can modify restriction "
"conditions, thresholds, and applicability rules."
msgstr "更新優惠券限制（僅限管理員）。可以修改限制條件、門檻和適用規則。"

msgid "Partially update restriction"
msgstr "部分更新限制"

msgid ""
"Update specific restriction fields (admin only). Useful for adjusting "
"thresholds or conditions without resending full restriction data."
msgstr "更新特定限制欄位（僅限管理員）。用於調整門檻或條件，而無需重新傳送完整的限制資料。"

msgid "Remove restriction"
msgstr "移除限制"

msgid ""
"Remove a restriction from a voucher (admin only). This makes the voucher "
"less restrictive and may increase its applicability."
msgstr "從優惠券中移除限制（僅限管理員）。這會使優惠券的限制減少，可能會提高其適用性。"

msgid "List applied vouchers in cart"
msgstr "列出購物車中已套用的優惠券"

msgid ""
"Get all vouchers currently applied to the authenticated user's cart. Shows "
"voucher codes, discount amounts, and application status."
msgstr "取得目前套用到已驗證用戶購物車的所有優惠券。顯示優惠券代碼、折扣金額和套用狀態。"

msgid "Apply voucher to cart"
msgstr "將優惠券套用至購物車"

msgid ""
"Apply a voucher to the user's cart. Validates voucher eligibility, "
"calculates discount, and adds to cart. Returns error if voucher is invalid "
"or already applied."
msgstr "將優惠券套用至用戶的購物車。驗證優惠券的資格，計算折扣，並加入購物車。如果優惠券無效或已經套用，則返回錯誤。"

msgid "Get applied voucher details"
msgstr "取得已套用優惠券詳情"

msgid ""
"Get detailed information about a specific voucher applied to cart including "
"discount amount, voucher code, and application timestamp."
msgstr "取得套用至購物車的特定優惠券的詳細資訊，包括折扣金額、優惠券代碼和套用時間戳。"

msgid "Update applied voucher"
msgstr "更新已套用優惠券"

msgid ""
"Update an applied voucher in the cart. Can refresh discount calculation if "
"cart contents changed."
msgstr "在購物車中更新已套用的優惠券。如果購物車內容有所更改，可以重新計算折扣。"

msgid "Partially update applied voucher"
msgstr "部分更新已套用優惠券"

msgid ""
"Update specific fields of an applied voucher. Useful for recalculating "
"discounts without full voucher reapplication."
msgstr "更新已套用優惠券的特定欄位。可用於在不重新套用整個優惠券的情況下重新計算折扣。"

msgid "Remove voucher from cart"
msgstr "從購物車移除優惠券"

msgid ""
"Remove a voucher from the cart. Discount is recalculated without this "
"voucher. User can reapply the same voucher later if still eligible."
msgstr "從購物車中移除優惠券。不包含此優惠券重新計算折扣。如果用戶仍符合資格，之後可以再次套用相同的優惠券。"

msgid "Apply voucher code to cart"
msgstr "將優惠券碼套用至購物車"

msgid ""
"Apply a voucher to cart by entering voucher code. Validates code, checks "
"eligibility, prevents duplicate application, and calculates discount. "
"Returns applied voucher details or error message."
msgstr "透過輸入優惠券代碼將優惠券套用至購物車。驗證代碼、檢查資格、防止重複套用，並計算折扣。返回套用的優惠券詳細資訊或錯誤訊息。"

